      <p class="paper-note"><b style="color:#539bf5;">Note:</b> This paper introduce IMAGINE. An autotelic agent that learns to represent and to target goals with language by interacting with a Social Partner. By internalizing language production it is able to compose new goals during exploration.  </p>
